    ;; ── ESP32-C6-MINI-1 / MINI-1U ────────────────────────────────────────────
    ;; MINI-1 = PCB trace antenna (default populated)
    ;; MINI-1U = U.FL external antenna connector (alternate BOM)
    ;; Both share IDENTICAL footprint: castellation 2×12+2 1.27mm pitch
    ;; Antenna selection handled by 0Ω resistors R_ANT_PCB / R_ANT_EXT
    ;; C6 GPIO: Thread/Matter/Zigbee co-exist with WiFi6 and BLE5
