  ;;
  ;; ── Design notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  ;;
  (text "ESP32-C6 RADIO CO-PROCESSOR NOTES:\n\nANTENNA SELECTION (Espressif HW Design Guidelines §RF):\n  R_ANT_PCB (0Ω, populated): routes C6 RF pad to MINI-1 PCB trace antenna\n  R_ANT_EXT (0Ω, DNP):       routes C6 RF pad to J_ANT U.FL connector\n  Only ONE resistor may be populated. Never both simultaneously.\n  PCB RF trace: 50Ω impedance controlled, outer layer only, no vias, 135° bends\n  Keepout under J_ANT U.FL: all layers clear per Espressif guideline\n\nMODULE SELECTION:\n  Default BOM: ESP32-C6-MINI-1-N4 (PCB antenna, 4MB flash)\n  Alternate:   ESP32-C6-MINI-1U-N4 (U.FL connector, same footprint)\n  To use external antenna: swap to MINI-1U, populate R_ANT_EXT, DNP R_ANT_PCB\n  Connect pigtail + 2.4GHz antenna to J_ANT\n\nPCB PLACEMENT (CRITICAL — Espressif HW guideline):\n  C6 module placed at carrier PCB EDGE with antenna overhanging the board\n  Feed point of antenna close to board edge\n  No copper (any layer) within 3mm of antenna trace\n  No HUB75 CLK/LAT traces within 10mm of antenna\n  No power switching traces (TPS54331 PH node) within 15mm of antenna\n\nSPI SLAVE INTERFACE:\n  CS_C6_MCU (GPIO18): chip select from STM32U585 (MCU)\n  CS_C6_MPU (GPIO19): chip select from QRB2210 (MPU)\n  MOSI/MISO/SCK: shared with S3 SPI bus — separate CS lines arbitrate\n\nUART TO ESP32-S3 (direct link, independent of UNO Q):\n  S3_C6_TX → C6 GPIO4 (RX): S3 pushes display events, MQTT payloads\n  S3_C6_RX → C6 GPIO5 (TX): not used on this carrier (C6→S3 via SPI)\n  See design spec §S3↔C6 Direct Link for architecture rationale\n\nMCU UART (GPIO16/17 default):\n  STM32U585 UART for AT-command style control of WiFi/BLE\n  499Ω series resistor recommended on TX line (suppress 80MHz harmonics)\n  Per Espressif HW guideline §UART\n\nUSB-C J_C6_USB:\n  C6 has built-in USB-Serial/JTAG — no external bridge chip needed\n  Use for C6 firmware flashing and debug logging\n  CC1/CC2: 5.1kΩ to GND (USB device identification)"
    (at 20 130 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top)))
)
